Ethereum amount formatting utilities for converting raw values to human-readable formats.

- Use `toReadableAmount()` for user-facing display with proper decimal handling
- Default to 18 decimals for ETH values, customize for other tokens
- Always handle both number and bigint inputs for compatibility
- Strip trailing zeros from formatted amounts for clean display